PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1980-2753 which will permit the Minister to enter into Agreements with individual Indians for the repayment of housing loans guaranteed by the Minister under the INDIAN ON-RESERVE LOAN GUARANTEE PROGRAM, and to reduce the original interest rates.
